import React from 'react';
import {
  Box,
  Container,
  Grid,
  Typography,
  Link,
  IconButton,
} from '@mui/material';
import {
  Facebook,
  Twitter,
  Instagram,
  YouTube,
} from '@mui/icons-material';

const Footer = () => {
  return (
    <Box
      component="footer"
      sx={{
        py: 6,
        px: 2,
        mt: 'auto',
        background: 'rgba(0,0,0,0.8)',
        borderTop: '1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1)',
        backdropFilter: 'blur(10px)',
      }}
    >
      <Container maxWidth="lg">
        <Grid container spacing={4}>
          <Grid item xs={12} sm={4}>
            <Typography variant="h6" color="white" gutterBottom>
              Cosmos Shop
            </Typography>
            <Typography variant="body2" color="white">
              Your one-stop destination for all things astronomical.
              Explore the universe from your doorstep.
            </Typography>
          </Grid>
          <Grid item xs={12} sm={4}>
            <Typography variant="h6" color="white" gutterBottom>
              Quick Links
            </Typography>
            <Link href="/products" color="inherit" display="block" sx={{ mb: 1 }}>Products</Link>
            <Link href="/about" color="inherit" display="block" sx={{ mb: 1 }}>About Us</Link>
            <Link href="/contact" color="inherit" display="block" sx={{ mb: 1 }}>Contact</Link>
            <Link href="/shipping" color="inherit" display="block" sx={{ mb: 1 }}>Shipping Info</Link>
          </Grid>
          <Grid item xs={12} sm={4}>
            <Typography variant="h6" color="white" gutterBottom>
              Connect With Us
            </Typography>
            <Box>
              <IconButton color="inherit" sx={{ '&:hover': { color: '#1877f2' } }}>
                <Facebook />
              </IconButton>
              <IconButton color="inherit" sx={{ '&:hover': { color: '#1da1f2' } }}>
                <Twitter />
              </IconButton>
              <IconButton color="inherit" sx={{ '&:hover': { color: '#c13584' } }}>
                <Instagram />
              </IconButton>
              <IconButton color="inherit" sx={{ '&:hover': { color: '#ff0000' } }}>
                <YouTube />
              </IconButton>
            </Box>
            <Typography variant="body2" color="white" sx={{ mt: 2 }}>
              Subscribe to our newsletter for updates and special offers!
            </Typography>
          </Grid>
        </Grid>
        <Typography variant="body2" color="white" align="center" sx={{ mt: 4 }}>
          {new Date().getFullYear()} Cosmos Shop. All rights reserved.
        </Typography>
      </Container>
    </Box>
  );
};

export default Footer;
